LazuriteBuff: {
	Title: Oceanic Absorption
	Description: If any entity in the area of attack has certain debuffs, this item will be empowered and spread the absorbed debuff onto nearby enemies.
}

InsurgentBuff: {
	Title: Ethereal Bond
	Description: This item allows you to consume a fraction of your health in exchange for power. Consumed health is stored as Ethereal Bond and is restored when you satisfy a certain condition, however, it is lost if you switch the item.
}

BasaltBuff: {
	Title: Tectonic Resonance
	Description: This item will be empowered and gain new abilities while in Underworld Domain or under certain circumstances...
}

